g.text: Gambia released an estimated 1.88 MtCO2e in 2023 (excl. LULUCF), a change of -1.5 % compared to the previous year. Per capita
GHG emissions were 0.68 tCO2e in 2023. Cumulative CO2 emissions since 1850 were 0.124 GtCO2, or about 0% of global emissions
to date. Sources: EDGAR v9, GCB 2023, UNFCCC, Grassi et al. 2021
